@startuml Sequence_Comment_Vote
title Sequence Diagram - Bình luận & Vote (UC6 + UC7)

actor User as U
participant "Lesson Page" as V
participant "CommentController" as CMC
database "Database" as DB

== Xem Comments ==
U -> V : Xem comments của Lesson
V -> CMC : GET /lesson/{id}/comments
CMC -> DB : SELECT FROM comments\nWHERE lesson_id = ?\nJOIN users ON user_id
DB --> CMC : List<Comment> with User info
CMC --> V : Render comments\n(threaded by parent_id)
V --> U : Hiển thị danh sách comments

== Viết Comment ==
U -> V : Viết comment mới
V -> CMC : POST /comment\n(content, lesson_id, parent_id)
CMC -> DB : INSERT INTO comments\n(content, lesson_id, user_id, parent_id, created_at)
DB --> CMC : OK
CMC --> V : Refresh danh sách comments
V --> U : Cập nhật hiển thị

== Vote Comment ==
U -> V : Nhấn Like/Dislike
V -> CMC : POST /comment/{id}/vote\n(is_like)
CMC -> DB : SELECT FROM comment_votes\nWHERE comment_id = ? AND user_id = ?
DB --> CMC : CommentVote / null

alt Chưa vote trước đó
    CMC -> DB : INSERT INTO comment_votes\n(is_like, comment_id, user_id)
    DB --> CMC : OK
else Đã vote cùng loại (toggle off)
    CMC -> DB : DELETE FROM comment_votes\nWHERE id = ?
    DB --> CMC : OK
else Đã vote khác loại (switch)
    CMC -> DB : UPDATE comment_votes\nSET is_like = ?\nWHERE id = ?
    DB --> CMC : OK
end

CMC --> V : Cập nhật vote count
V --> U : Hiển thị vote mới

@enduml
